 more than 300 family medicine residents have been trained through the program who now practice family medicine and various subspecialties in Rockford, throughout Illinois, across the nation and around the world. I invite you to learn more about our program. Curriculum We are committed to the ideals of our discipline of family medicine and are proud of the educational experience we provide in this unopposed residency program. We invite you to take a closer look at the Rockford Family Medicine Residency Program. Learn More Salary and Benefits The health and well-being of our residents is important to us. We offer a competitive salary and benefits package and perks to keep you and your family happy and healthy. Learn More application We strive to recruit top-notch medical students who will become excellent family medicine physicians. Learn more about our eligibility criteria to see if you meet the requirements and, if so, we invite you to apply to our outstanding residency program. Learn More Discover Rockford Discover the many reasons Rockford, Illinois, is a great choice to work, live and play. Learn More UI Health L.P. Johnson Family Health Center The UI Health L.P. Johnson Family Health Center serves patients of all ages at a unique family practice that is a teaching facility associated with the University of Illinois College of Medicine Rockford. Learn More SwedishAmerican Hospital The residency program is affiliated with SwedishAmerican: A Division of UW Health with core rotations at the award-winning SwedishAmerican Hospital where we enjoy the full support of hospital administration and medical staff. Learn More Current Residents Faculty Contact Us About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective and Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients  Businesses and Community RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!    If you h